FBIS4-59514 "drnes094_j_94006" FBIS-NES-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Roundup of 13-16 May Clashes in North, South Roundup of 13-16 May Clashes in North, South Al-Dali' Citizens Vow Loyalty JN1305174894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 13 May 94 JN1305174894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN ["Text" of cable from "al-Dali' District citizens" to Presidential Council Chairman Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih; date not given] [Text] Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, Presidential Council chairman, supreme commander of the Armed Forces, and secretary general of the General People's Congress: From al-Dali', and in the name of thousands of town residents, and in the name of the committees for defending unity and confronting secession, we announce to you that all citizens of al-Dali' are standing in the same trench with the Armed Forces of Constitutional legitimacy, who smashed the strongholds of the forces of apostasy and secession and taught them a lesson they will never forget. We have joined our Armed Forces, who are heading toward Lahij to sweep out the other dens of the secessionists. Proceed forward and we will march behind you, and God will grant success to all of us. [Signed] Citizens of al-Dali' District
